NAME
    nibbler - snake game

SYNOPSIS
    ./nibbler width height [OPTIONS]...

DESCRIPTION
    Snake game made in C++.

    --help display this help and exit

    width
        The width of the Snake board. Must be between 30 (inclusive) and 100 (inclusive)

    height
        The height of the Snake board. Must be between 30 (inclusive) and 100 (inclusive)

    -e, --endless
        Each map doesn't have a finish score and will end only when one of the players are dead

    --nff, --nofriendlyfire, --no-friendly-fire
        The players cannot die while trying to eat themself or another player

EXAMPLES
    Start a Snake with a board of 50x50:
        ./nibbler 50 50

    Start a Snake with a board of 75x75 and endless maps:
        ./nibbler 75 75 -e
        ./nibbler 75 75 --endless

    Start a Snake with a board of 60x60 and without friendly fire:
        ./nibbler 60 60 --nff
        ./nibbler 60 60 --nofriendlyfire
        ./nibbler 60 60 --no-friendly-fire

AUTHORS
    dleblond and mnguyen
